2026-05-11T21:38:44.3123959Z 21    <!--
2026-05-11T21:38:44.3124332Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-11T21:38:44.3124517Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-11T21:38:44.3124860Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-11T21:38:44.3125191Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-11T21:38:44.3125531Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T21:38:44.3125853Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
